<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٠٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى بْنُ سَعِيدٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4035">ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4385">عَطَاءٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا نَعْزِلُ عَلَى عَهْدِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>